name: PRAutolabeler & Releases Drafter
description:
Automate Drafts your next release notes as Pull Requests are merged into main brach.
Version Release be resolved automatically based on labels of individual pull requests.
Append the following file 'https://github.com/pagonxt/.github/blob/master/.github/release-drafter.yml' into your .github folder.
 Oficial Project and Docs: https://github.com/release-drafter/release-drafter
